20for%20alleged%20derogatory%20posts%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20his%20son%20and%20state%20minister%20Nara%20Lokesh%20and%20daughter-in-law%20Brahmini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20complaint%20by%20a%20local%20leader%20of%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%2C%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Varma%20at%20Maddipadu%20Police%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%20Mandal%20Parishad%20Secretary%20Ramalingam%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20controversial%20filmmaker%2C%20who%20had%20made%20the%20alleged%20derogatory%20comments%20last%20year%20against%20then%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20his%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20filed%20a%20case%20under%20IT%20Act%20and%20took%20up%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERGV%2C%20as%20the%20director%20is%20popularly%20known%2C%20had%20made%20the%20comments%20on%20social%20media%20as%20part%20of%20the%20promotions%20for%20his%20movie%20'Vyuham'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20events%20that%20led%20to%20tragic%20death%20of%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20YS%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20in%20a%20helicopter%20crash%20in%202009%20and%20subsequent%20formation%20of%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20by%20his%20son%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20the%20movie%20was%20released%20late%20last%20year%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20simultaneous%20polls%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidered%20close%20to%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20RGV%20has%20been%20a%20bitter%20critic%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20He%20had%20earlier%20made%20the%20movie%20'Lakshmi's%20NTR'%20on%20the%20love%20and%20marriage%20of%20TDP%20founder%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20NT%20Rama%20Rao%20(NTR)%20with%20Lakshmi%20Parvathi.%20The%20film%20also%20portrayed%20the%20controversial%20role%20of%20NTR's%20son-in-law%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20who%20had%20led%20a%20revolt%20against%20NTR%20in%201995%20to%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%