y%20said%20he%20will%20support%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20didn't%20reveal%20much%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20then%20reassured%20President%20Zelensky%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20help%20Ukraine%20via%20his%20Starlink%20satellite%20constellation.%20Since%20the%20Russian%20invasion%20in%202022%2C%20Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink%20satellite%20system%20has%20provided%20Ukraine%20with%20significant%20frontline%20advantage%20by%20allowing%20its%20armed%20forces%20to%20share%20real-time%20drone%20coordinates%2C%20data%20and%20footage%20between%20units.%20It%20also%20gave%20Ukraine's%20military%20communications%20support%20in%20areas%20where%20mobile%20phone%20networks%20were%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fab1idtb8_trump-zelenskyy-reuters_625x300_27_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20and%20Trump%20had%20met%20recently%20in%20New%20York%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20meet%20in%20September.%20The%20two%20leaders%20had%20discussed%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20war%20with%20Russia%20could%20end%20and%20a%20diplomatic%20solution%20be%20found.%20%26quot%3BI%20promise%20you%20will%20be%20happy%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20had%20reportedly%20told%20Zelensky%20at%20that%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPUTIN%20AND%20ZELENSKY'S%20DEMANDS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20president%20had%20recently%20demanded%20that%20Ukraine%20withdraw%20from%20swathes%20of%20its%20eastern%20and%20southern%20territory%20as%20a%20precondition%20to%20peace%20talks.%20The%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20that%20people%20familiar%20with%20%26quot%3BThursday's%20call%26quot%3B%20said%20Trump%20had%20briefly%20raised%20the%20question%20of%20land%20with%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C