0and%20dismantling%20its%20associated%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20thingQbator%20programme%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98thingQbator%E2%80%99%20began%20in%202018%20as%20a%20maker%20space%20for%20Cisco%E2%80%99s%20engineers%20to%20don%20their%20innovation%20caps%20and%20transform%20their%20ideas%20into%20working%20prototypes.%20The%20success%20of%20this%20internal%20incubator%20prompted%20the%20company%20to%20scale%20it%20up%20in%20partnership%20with%20nasscom%20foundation%20and%20open%20it%20to%20universities%20across%20the%20country%20to%20promote%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20encompasses%20a%20four-stage%20programme%2C%20nurturing%20the%20transformation%20of%20ideas%20into%20thriving%20ventures.%20From%20the%20ideation%20stage%20to%20incubation%2C%20the%20top%2010%20teams%20are%20granted%20a%20seed%20fund%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20marking%20the%20transition%20of%20their%20social%20ventures%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seventh%20edition%20of%20thingQbator%20is%20currently%20underway%2C%20mentoring%20and%20nurturing%20undergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20students%20with%20a%20vision%20aligned%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%E2%80%99%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20incubating%20new%20startups%2C%20thingQbator%20also%20offers%20a%20myriad%20of%20learning%20opportunities%20for%20students%20across%20the%20country.%20This%20learning%20platform%20offers%20over%2018%20courses%20in%20hardware%20and%20software%20that%20students%20can%20complete%20at%20their%20convenience%20to%20enhance%20their%20technical%20skills.%20This%20platform%20is%20available%20to%20all%20students%20who%20register.%20The%20courses%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%20%E2%80%94%20from%20building%20apps%20using%20Flutter%20to%20creating%20websites%2C%20web%20development%20skills%2C%20and%20working%20with%20Raspberry%20Pi%203%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20a%20high%20level%20of%20technical%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2030%2C000%20course%20completion%20certificates%20have%20been%20issued%2C%20and%20over%2016%2C000%20unique%20students%20have%20received%20course%20completion%20certificates%20as%20of%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20a%20platform%20that%20transcends%20entrepreneurial%20incubation%2C%20thingQbator%20is%20empowering%20young%20Indians%20to%20become%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20technology%20and%20innovation.%20This%20initiative%20serves%20as%20a%20powerful%20catalyst%2C%20propelling%20the%20vision%20of%20a%20technologically%20advanced%20and%20socially%20empowered%20India%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20truly%20believe%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20ignite%20the%20imaginations%20of%20young%20minds%2C%20and%20universities%20and%20other%20educational%20institutions%20are%20the%20ideal%20environments%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20explore%20new%20ideas.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20aim%20to%20do%20through%20our%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20we%20collaborate%20with%20universities%20to%20identify%20and%20mentor%20young%20minds%2C%20helping%20them%20shape%20and%20realize%20their%20entrepreneurial%20aspirations.%20This%20initiative%20is%20not%20just%20about%20nurturing%20startups%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20empowering%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20innovators%20to%20create%20impactful%20solutions%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Harish%20Krishnan%2C%20Managing%20Director%20%26amp%3B%20Chief%20Policy%20Officer%2C%20Cisco%20India%20%26amp%3B%20SAARC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20%26amp%3B%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20nasscom%20foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731321261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D378406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Cisco%20and%20nasscom%20foundation%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20nurtures%20young%20innovators%20by%20providing%20mentorship%2C%20funding%2C%20and%20resources%20to%20solve%20societal%20issues%20using%20technology.%20Since%202018%2C%20it%20has%20incubated%20over%2058%20startups%2C%20addressing%20challenges%20in%20education%2C%20agriculture%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20accessibility%2C%20empowering%20students%20to%20become%20job%20creators%20and%20future-ready%20entrepreneurs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah's%20Promise%20In%20Jharkhand%3A%20If%20%26quot%3BIntruder%26quot%3B%20Marries%20Tribal%2C%20Can't%20Get%20Land%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20'intruder'%20who%20marries%20a%20girl%20from%20a%20tribal%20community%20will%20not%20be%20entitled%20to%20land%20in%20her%20name%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20in%20poll-bound%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20jabs%20at%20the%20ruling%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha-Congress%20alliance%2C%20he%20said%20if%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20wins%2C%20it%20will%20pass%20a%20law%20to%20stop%20transfer%20of%20land%20to%20'intruders'%20-%20the%20reference%20was%20to%20'infiltrators'%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20an%20echo%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20comments%20-%20who%20marry%20tribal%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInfiltrators%20are%20grabbing%20land%20by%20marrying%20our%20daughters.%20We%20will%20bring%20a%20law%20to%20prevent%20transfer%20of%20land%20to%20infiltrators%20if%20they%20marry%20tribal%20women.%20We%20will%20also%20form%20a%20committee%20to%20identify%20infiltrators%20to%20drive%20them%20out%20and%20reclaim%20land%20grabbed%20by%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Seraikela.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20follows%20a%20similar%20broadside%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20last%20week.%20Mr%20Modi%20was%20speaking%20in%20Garhwa%20where%20he%20slammed%20into%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren's%20administration%2C%20accusing%20the%20ruling%20JMM%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bsupporters%20of%20Bangladesh%20infiltrators%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-jharkhand-election-pm-narendra-modi-pms-infiltrator-jab-at-hemant-sorens-party-congress-in-jharkhand-rally-6940229%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPM's%20%26quot%3BInfiltrator%26quot%3B%20Jab%20At%20Hemant%20Soren's%20Party%2C%20Congress%20In%20Jharkhand%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20JMM-RJD-Congress%20government%20has%20taken%20appeasement%20to%20its%20peak.%20These%20parties%20are%20destroying%20the%20state's%20social%20harmony.%20They%20are%20supporters%20of%20infiltrators.%20To%20get%20votes%20of%20Bangladesh%20infiltrators%2C%20they%20are%20getting%20them%20settled%20across%20Jharkhand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20JMM%20over%20%26quot%3Bthe%20way%20Champai%20Soren%20was%20humiliated%20and%20thrown%20out%26quot%3B%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20just%20an%20insult%20to%20Champai%20Soren%20but%20an%20insult%20to%20tribal%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChampai%20Soren%20was%20a%20former%20JM%20leader%20who%20was%20made%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%20arrested%20and%20jailed%20on%20corruption%20charges%2C%20but%20removed%20immediately%20after%20the%20party%20boss%20got%20bail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%20and%20his%20induction%C2%A0has%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20boost%20for%20the%20party's%20efforts%20to%20strengthen%20its%20connection%20with%20the%20tribal%20communities%2C%20a%20strong%20support%20base%20of%20the%20JMM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-jharkhand-chief-minister-champai-soren-joins-bjp-days-after-quitting-jmm-6452505%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEx%20Chief%20Minister%20Champai%20Soren%20Joins%20BJP%20Days%20After%20Quitting%20JMM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChampai%20Soren%20was%20also%20referenced%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20accused%20the%20JMM%20and%20Congress%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bleft%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20humiliating%20an%20Adivasi%20son%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20corrupt%20leaders%20of%20the%20JMM-Congress%20alliance%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20further%20said%2C%20would%20be%20jailed%20if%20the%20BJP%20wins%20back%20power%20in%20the%20mineral%20and%20coal-rich%20state%2C%20accusing%20the%20incumbent%20government%20of%20a%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20jobs%20scam%2C%20a%20Rs%20300%20crore%20land%20scam%2C%20and%20a%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20mining%20scam%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20is%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20it%20would%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20central%20government%20sends%20Rs%201%20(as%20aid)%2025%20paise%20is%20added%20to%20it%20by%20the%20state...%20so%20Rs%201.25%20reaches%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20headline%20seizure%20of%20cash%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20when%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20raided%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Dhiraj%20Sahu's%20home%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcash-haul-linked-to-congress-mp-dhiraj-prasad-sahu-crosses-rs-351-crore-counting-still-on-4651881%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bhighest-ever%26quot%3B%20recovery%20of%20over%20Rs%20350%20crore%20in%20a%20single%20operation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ask%20all%20of%20you...%20has%20anyone%20seen%20Rs%20350%20crore%3F%20But%20Rs%20350%20crore%20was%20found%20at%20the%20house%20of%20a%20Congress%20MP.%2