%20return%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office%20just%20weeks%20away%2C%20some%20in%20India%20are%20already%20hoping%20that%20he%20will%20put%20New%20Delhi's%20new%20adversary%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20in%20his%20place.%20After%20all%2C%20Trump's%20past%20comments%20on%20Trudeau%20range%20from%20%E2%80%9Cweak%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-faced%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20even%20%E2%80%9Cfar-left%20lunatic%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94hardly%20a%20subtle%20hint%20of%20his%20opinion%20of%20his%20neighbouring%20country's%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Canadians%20Are%20Worried%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Canadians%2C%20though%2C%20Trump's%20second%20term%20has%20sparked%20more%20shock%20than%20celebration.%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Chrystia%20Freeland%20(also%20the%20country's%20finance%20minister)%20held%20two%20press%20conferences%20post%20his%20election%20to%20calm%20Canadian%20nerves%2C%20saying%20Canada%20will%20be%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20fine%E2%80%9D.%20Yet%2C%20many%20Canadians%20remain%20uneasy%20over%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20for%20good%20reason.%20There%20are%20three%20big%20areas%20of%20anxiety%3A%20tariffs%2C%20NATO%20contributions%20and%20the%20looming%20renegotiation%20of%20the%20US-Mexico-Canada%20Agreement%20(USMCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Trump%20has%20hinted%20at%20slapping%20a%20blanket%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20all%20imports%20to%20the%20US%2C%20which%20would%20hit%20Canada%20hard%20given%20that%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20its%20exports%20are%20US-bound.%20Then%20there%20is%20Trump's%20expectation%20that%20NATO%20members%20chip%20in%20a%20full%202%25%20of%20their%20GDP%20on%20defence.%20Canada%20is%20currently%20far%20behind%20and%20contributing%20only%201.23%25%E2%80%94a%20potential%20sticking%20point%20if%20Trump%20insists%20on%20the%20required%20contributions%20like%20he%20did%20during%20the%20last%20term.%20Lastly%2C%20there's%20the%20USMCA%2C%20which%20Trump%20himself%20strong-armed%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20into%20renegotiating%20in%202020.%20Trump%20has%20hinted%20that%20the%20deal%20is%20set%20for%20review%20in%202026.%20Canadians%20worry%20that%20the%20President-elect%20could%20push%20for%20even%20stricter%20terms%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20Trump%20Side%20With%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20team%20and%20its%20Western%20European%20pals%20are%20clearly%20frustrated%20with%20India's%20refusal%20to%20oppose%20Russia%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20They%20have%20not%20said%20it%20out%20loud%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20suspect%20that%20they%20are%20quietly%20backing%20Trudeau%20behind%20the%20scenes%20in%20his%20finger-pointing%20at%20India%2C%20accusing%20officials%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20separatist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20Let's%20be%20real%E2%80%94it%20wasn't%20without%20Big%20Brother's%20nod%20that%20Trudeau%20stood%20in%20Parliament%20last%20year%20hurling%20accusations%20at%20India.%20Furthermore%2C%20if%20Canada%20decides%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20these%20allegations%2C%20the%20possibility%20is%20it%20won't%20be%20acting%20alone.%20The%20US%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20key%20members%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20alliance%2C%20have%20often%20helped%20manage%20diplomatic%20and%20security%20issues%20with%20countries%20outside%20the%20alliance.%20Since%20both%20countries%20have%20close%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20they%20may%20help%20Canada%20weigh%20the%20strength%20and%20possible%20impact%20of%20these%20accusations%20before%20taking%20any%20official%20steps.%20Still%2C%20accusing%20a%20powerful%20country%20like%20India%20could%20affect%20important%20strategic%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20possible%20egging%20on%20by%20Big%20Brother%20suits%20Trudeau%20too%2C%20giving%20him%20a%20shot%20at%20placating%20his%20Sikh%20voter%20base%20and%20propping%20up%20his%20waning%20popularity.%20However%2C%20only%20a%20rookie%20diplomat%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20can%20fully%20trust%20the%20self-serving%20strategy%20that%20the%20US%20usually%20follows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20cannot%20underplay%20US%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller's%20blunt%20statement%20last%20month%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Canadian%20matter%2C%20we%20have%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20allegations%20are%20extremely%20serious%20and%20they%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20seriously.%20We%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20government%20of%20India%20cooperate%20with%20Canada%20in%20its%20investigation.%20Obviously%2C%20they%20have%20not%20chosen%20that%20path.%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0The%20statement%20did%20not%20reflect%20India's%20position%20that%20there%20was%20complete%20disregard%20for%20New%20Delhi's%20request%20to%20Ottawa%20to%20share%20evidence.%20And%20now%2C%20with%20allegations%20of%20India's%20involvement%20in%20an%20attempted%20assassination%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20another%20card%20to%20play.%20Nonetheless%2C%20India%20is%20cooperating%20with%20the%20US%20on%20the%20investigation%20and%20neither%20side%20wants%20to%20blow%20it%20out%20of%20proportion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20Trump%20re-enters%20his%20office%2C%20his%20promise%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20if%20fulfilled%2C%20will%20be%20a%20game-changer.%20Without%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20equation%2C%20the%20US%20pressure%20on%20India%20to%20pick%20a%20side%20goes%20out%20of%20the%20window%2C%20and%20Biden's%20%E2%80%9Ccold-shoulder%E2%80%9D%20tactics%20would%20become%20a%20non-issue.%20Trump%2C%20however%2C%20we%20all%20know%2C%20is%20a%20wildcard.%20While%20he%20may%20want%20closer%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20we%20know%20how%20that%20%E2%80%9CAmerica%20First%E2%80%9D%20agenda%20translates%3A%20tariffs%2C%20immigration%20restrictions%20and%20a%20hard%20line%20on%20H-1B%20visas.%20Fortunately%20though%2C%20Trump's%20stance%20on%20Russia%20(to%20end%20the%20war)%20aligns%20with%20India's%2C%20as%20does%20his%20anti-China%20focus.%20It's%20quite%20possible%20he%20might%20ask%20Trudeau%20to%20either%20produce%20proof%20in%20the%20Nijjar%20case%20or%20drop%20the%20offensive.%20Who%20knows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20Don't%20Underestimate%20US-Canada%20Bond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20we%20should%20never%20underestimate%20America's%20deep-rooted%20ties%20with%20Canada%E2%80%94they%20are%20in%20a%20league%20of%20their%20own.%20Sure%2C%20Trump%20and%20Trudeau%20have%20clashed%20publicly%2C%20but%20Trudeau%20is%20not%20one%20to%20be%20caught%20off%20guard.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20he%20revealed%20that%20his%20officials%20had%20been%20quietly%20talking%20to%20Trump's%20campaign%20team%20for%20months%2C%20readying%20for%20a%20potential%20return.%20Trudeau%20didn't%20waste%20a%20minute%E2%80%94he%20reinstated%20a%20Cabinet%20committee%20on%20US-Canada%20relations%2C%20led%20by%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Chrystia%20Freeland%2C%20to%20deal%20with%20anything%20Trump%202.0%20might%20throw%20at%20them.%20And%20he%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20call%20Trump%20after%20the%20win%2C%20showing%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Trudeau%20is%20all%20about%20pragmatism%2C%20or%2C%20dare%20I%20say%2C%20even%20subservience.%20His%20office%20spelt%20it%20out%20well%3A%20%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%20election%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20a%20second%20term%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20will%20focus%20on%20critical%20Canada-US%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US-Canada%20relationship%20is%20unlike%20anything%20else%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20two%20countries%20are%20more%20like%20siblings%20rather%20than%20neighbours%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20sits%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%20They%20are%20two%20very%20prosperous%20countries%3A%20Canada's%20per%20capita%20income%20is%20over%20%2458%2C000%2C%20while%20America's%20is%20%2481%2C000.%20They%20have%20got%20each%20other's%20backs%20on%20defence%2C%20border%20security%2C%20and%20law%20enforcement.%20The%20overlap%20is%20everywhere%E2%80%94from%20culture%20and%20sports%20to%20leisure%20and%20shared%20traditions.%20They%20have%20much%20more%20in%20common%20between%20them%20than%20either%20of%20them%20has%20with%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20this%3A%20in%202023%2C%20the%20US-Canada%20trade%20hit%20over%20a%20trillion%20dollars%2C%20with%20%242.8%20billion%20crossing%20their%20border%20every%20single%20day.%20They%20are%20each%20other's%20biggest%20trade%20partners%2C%20with%20Canada%20sending%2078%25%20of%20its%20goods%20and%20services%20to%20the%20US%20every%20year%2C%20and%20over%20400%2C000%20people%20moving%20across%20their%20shared%205%2C525-mile%20border%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanada%20Has%20Five%20Eyes%20By%20Its%20Side%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20Canada%20is%20a%20NATO%20member%20and%20the%20countries%20in%20the%20grouping%20are%20quite%20united%20and%20usually%20back%20each%20other%20against%20any%20third%20party.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20intelligence-sharing%20bond%20under%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20institution.%20The%20Five%20Eyes%20alliance%E2%80%94a%20formidable%20network%20comprising%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand%E2%80%94has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20global%20intelligence%20operations%20for%20decades.%20The%20alliance%20was%20built%20to%20facilitate%20intelligence%20collection%20and%20sharing%20among%20its%20members%2C%20ensuring%20a%20near-seamless%20flow%20of%20critical%20security%20information.%20In%20light%20of%20Canada's%20recent%20allegations%20against%20Indian%20officials%2C%20the%20alliance%20ought%20to%20have%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20sharing%20information%20with%20Canadian%20intelligence%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20as%20a%20core%20member%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%2C%20Canada%20has%20access%20to%20intelligence%20and%20insights%20that%20most%20nations%20can%20only%20aspire%20to%20attain.%20If%20Canada%20believes%20it%20has%20intelligence%20linking%20Indian%20officials%20to%20Nijjar's%20assassination%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20benefiting%20from%20the%20information-sharing%20protocols%20within%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20network.%20Notably%2C%20Canada%20may%20be%20leveraging%20Five%20Eyes%20capabilities%20to%20cross-reference%20signals%20intelligence%20(SIGINT)%20and%20other%20classified%20insights%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20build%20a%20stronger%20case%20against%20India%2C%20should%20any%20concrete%20evidence%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20Canada's%20Voters%20Decide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20India%20might%20just%20have%20to%20play%20the%20waiting%20game%20until%20Canada's%20next%20general%20election%2C%20now%20less%20than%20a%20year%20away.%20Trudeau's%20grip%20on%20power%20since%20he%20took%20office%20in%202015%20is%20looking%20shakier%20than%20ever%20today.%20If%20he%20is%20out%20of%20the%20picture%2C%20the%20new%20government's%20stance%20on%20India%20could%20breathe%20fresh%20life%20into%20those%20frosty%20bilateral%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731315780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F58f320r_trump-canda_625x300_11_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-or-canada-which-way-will-trump-look-6992629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office%20just%20weeks%20away%2C%20some%20in%20India%20are%20already%20hoping%20that%20he%20will%20put%20New%20Delhis%20new%20adversary%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20in%20his%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-or-canada-which-way-will-trump-look-6992629%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dutch%20Police%20Use%20Hologram%20To%20Solve%202009%20Amsterdam%20Sex%20Worker's%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Netherlands%20Police%20are%20using%20an%20innovative%20life-size%20hologram%20of%20a%20sex%20worker%2C%20killed%20in%20Amsterdam%20in%20February%202009%2C%20to%20uncover%20new%20information%20about%20the%20cold%20case%20and%20bring%20her%20killer%20or%20killers%20to%20justice.%20The%20hologram%20has%20been%20placed%20behind%20a%20window%20in%20Amsterdam's%20Red%20Light%20district.%20Sitting%20on%20a%20stool%2C%20it%20looks%20at%20people%20passing%20by%20and%20appears%20to%20knock%20on%20the%20window.%20The%20glass%20fogs%20up%2C%20while%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Chelp%E2%80%9D%20appears%20on%20it%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F11%2F10%2Feurope%2Fdutch-police-hologram-sex-worker-cold-case-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hologram%20is%20modelled%20on%20Bernadett%20Szab%C3%B3%2C%20known%20as%20Betty%2C%20who%20was%20found%20murdered%20in%20the%20Dutch%20capital%20in%202009.%C2%A0Created%20using%203D%20visualisation%20technology%2C%20it%20also%20features%20a%20large%20dragon%20tattoo%20covering%20Betty's%20stomach%20and%20chest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20house%20in%20the%20area%20has%20been%20dedicated%20entirely%20to%20Betty's%20murder%2C%20with%20large%20stickers%20on%20the%20windows%20and%20TV%20screens%20showing%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20a%20documentary%20and%20images%20of%20the%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20holographic%20has%20been%20created%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people%2C%20who%20may%20have%20knowledge%20about%20the%20murder%20case%20but%20did%20not%20come%20forward%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20official%20statement%2C%20Benjamin%20van%20Gogh%2C%20coordinator%20of%20the%20Amsterdam%20Wanted%20and%20Missing%20Persons%20Team%2C%20noted%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20to%20determine%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20get%20possible%20witnesses%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20to%20share%20their%20information%20with%20us%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetty's%20hologram%20may%20create%20a%20certain%20connection%20with%20her%20and%20thus%20convince%20a%20person%20to%20come%20forward.%20In%20this%20type%20of%20case%2C%20we%20always%20try%20to%20put%20a%20face%20on%20a%20victim%2C%20so%20that%20informants%20know%20who%20they're%20doing%20it%20for%2C%20and%20the%20hologram%20is%20a%20way%20of%20taking%20this%20a%20step%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20CNN%20quoted%20the%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Dutch%20police%20said%20that%20Szab%C3%B3%20was%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20poverty%20in%20the%20Hungarian%20city%20of%20Ny%C3%ADregyh%C3%A1za%2C%20before%20shifting%20to%20Amsterdam%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018.%20After%20landing%20in%20the%20city%2C%20she%20began%20earning%20money%20as%20a%20sex%20worker%20in%20the%20red%20light%20district.%20After%20becoming%20pregnant%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20work%20throughout%20her%20pregnancy%20and%20later%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20son%20in%20November%202008.%20The%20child%20was%20later%20placed%20with%20a%20foster%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetty%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20the%20night%20of%20February%2019%2C%202009%2C%20when%20two%20of%20her%20fellow%20sex%20workers%20reached%20her%20workroom%20on%20Oudezijds%20Achterburgwal.%20They%20realised%20they%20didn't%20see%20her%20or%20hear%20the%20music%20she%20usually%20played.%20At%20around%201%20AM%2C%20they%20found%20her%20body%20stabbed%20dozens%20of%20times.%20She%20was%2019%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fnov%2F10%2Fdutch-police-use-hologram-to-try-to-solve-2009-sex-worker-killing%5C%22%3E%20The%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20police%20carried%20out%20a%20large-scale%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%2C%20monitoring%20CCTVs%20and%20interviewing%20witnesses.%20The%20case%20remained%20unsolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reward%20for%20any%20information%20related%20to%20the%20case%20has%20been%20hiked%20to%20%E2%82%AC30%2C000%20(around%20%2432%2C160).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731315720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fscq145k8_amsterdam-sex-workers-murder_625x300_11_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdutch-police-use-hologram-to-solve-2009-amsterdam-sex-workers-murder-6992272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Netherlands%20Police%20are%20using%20an%20innovative%20life-size%20hologram%20of%20a%20sex%20worker%2C%20killed%20in%20Amsterdam%20in%20February%202009%2C%20to%20uncover%20new%20information%20about%20the%20cold%20case%20and%20bring%20her%20killer%20or%20killers%20to%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdutch-police-use-hologram-to-solve-2009-amsterdam-sex-workers-murder-6992272%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Religion%20Encourages%20Pollution%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20On%20Crackers%20Amid%20Air%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20had%20sharp%20words%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdelhi-police%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Police%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20demanded%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20action%26quot%3B%20to%20stop%20the%20sale%20and%20bursting%20of%20firecrackers%20in%20the%20city%20-%20an%20annual%20activity%20that%20defies%20an%20existing%20ban%20-%20even%20days%20after%20Diwali%2C%20observing%20sharply%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20religion%20encourages%20pollution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20religion%20encourages%20any%20activity%20which%20creates%20pollution.%20If%20firecrackers%20are%20burst%20in%20this%20fashion...%20it%20also%20affects%20fundamental%20right%20to%20health%20of%20the%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%2C%20hearing%20a%20case%20on%20Delhi's%20yearly%20air%20quality%20crisis%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20demanded%20the%20Delhi%20government%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20a%20permanent%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%20-%20the%20chemical%20residue%20of%20which%20blankets%20the%20city%20in%20cloud%20of%20toxic%20smog%20that%20smothers%20residents%20and%20severely%20endangers%20their%20health%20-%20in%20the%20city%20by%20November%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20hearing%20follows%20last%20week's%20reprimand%20for%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20police%2C%20each%20of%20which%20was%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20explain%20to%20the%20court%20why%20they%20had%20failed%20to%20implement%20and%20enforce%20the%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%2C%20which%20is%20announced%20before%20Diwali%20every%20year%20and%20has%20little%20or%20no%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-notice-to-delhi-top-cop-for-not-implementing-firecracker-ban-6940542%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Steps%20Taken%3F%26quot%3B%20Court%20Pulls%20Up%20Delhi%20Govt%2C%20Cops%20On%20Cracker%20Ban%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20today%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20chief%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20explaining%20steps%20taken%20but%20the%20court%20-%20which%20earlier%20pointed%20out%20it%20appears%20quite%20obvious%20the%20ban%20had%2C%20so%20far%2C%20failed%20to%20work%20-%20was