new%20people%20and%20patrons%20who%20wanted%20to%20help.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20got%20our%20footing%20right%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20these%20artists%E2%80%99%20development%20also.%20So%2C%20we%20started%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducating%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20Rajasthani%20folk%20artists%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20fully%20funded%20artist%20residency%20where%20young%20children%20from%20across%20Rajasthan%20can%20gather%20to%20learn%20folk%20music%20from%20maestros%20and%20gurus.%20This%20initiative%20is%20groundbreaking%20because%2C%20unlike%20Indian%20classical%20music%2C%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20educational%20structure%20for%20folk%20music.%20Traditionally%2C%20it%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20orally%20through%20generations%2C%20with%20no%20written%20records%20to%20preserve%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residency%20spans%20seven%20days%20and%20includes%20nine%20classes%20covering%20various%20disciplines%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20vocals%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekamaicha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emurli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flute)%2C%20%3Cem%3Etandura%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tamboura)%2C%20and%20more.%20Currently%2C%20the%20programme%20works%20with%20three%20folk%20music%20communities%3A%20%3Cem%3ELanga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EMeghwal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EManganiyars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20allowing%20students%20to%20learn%20directly%20from%20master%20artists%20of%20these%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20dignitaries%20like%20Lakha%20Khan%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20and%20the%20maestro%20