m%20company%2C%20offering%20him%20help%20when%20he%20needed%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20three%20cottages%20were%20ready%2C%20a%20woodpecker%20began%20visiting%20us%2C%20pecking%20at%20the%20panes%20with%20impressive%20intensity.%20We%20would%20shoo%20it%20away%2C%20but%20it%20would%20return%2C%20moving%20from%20one%20cottage%20to%20the%20next.%E2%80%9D%20After%20several%20days%20of%20unsuccessfully%20trying%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20bird%20%E2%80%94%20Depi%20laughs%20that%20they%20even%20kept%20a%20carpenter%20at%20hand%20to%20repair%20the%20damages%20caused%20%E2%80%94%20he%20realised%20the%20woodpecker%20was%20trying%20to%20convey%20a%20message.%20There%20were%20termites%20in%20the%20wood!%20After%20treating%20the%20wood%20with%20medication%2C%20one%20day%2C%20the%20woodpecker%20stopped%20visiting%20Aashraya.%20Its%20job%20was%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAashraya-on-the-Ganga-7-1730289678.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20meals%20at%20Ashraya%20on%20the%20Ganga%20reflect%20local%20and%20indigenous%20culture%20and%20the%20produce%20for%20them%20is%20sourced%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20farms%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAashraya-on-the-Ganga-7-1730289678.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAashraya-on-the-Ganga-7-1730289678.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAashraya-on-the-Ganga-7-1730289678.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3